    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A morpher computes its current surface by summing weighted geometry elements from the base geometry and all target geometries. The position of a vertex on the surface is produced by adding the position vector of a point on the base geometry to the position vectors of the corresponding points on all target geometries. The morpherâ€™s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnmorpher/1523754-calculationmode"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property selects the formula used to calculate this sum."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If the mode is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnmorphercalculationmode/scnmorphercalculationmodenormalized"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", the position from the base geometry is weighted by one minus the sum of all target weights, as in the following formula:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeListing",
          "code": [
            "Position = (1 - weight0 - weight1 - ...) * Base + weight0 * Target0 + weight1 * Target1 + ..."
          ],
          "syntax": "occ",
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "2557197",
            "title": "Listing 1"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If the mode is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnmorphercalculationmode/scnmorphercalculationmodeadditive"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", the position from the base geometry is not weighted, and SceneKit uses the following formula instead:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeListing",
          "code": [
            "Position = Base + weight0 * Target0 + weight1 * Target1 + ..."
          ],
          "syntax": "occ",
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "2557200",
            "title": "Listing 2"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
